Package service

Class AppointmentOutcomeService

java.lang.Object
service.AppointmentOutcomeService
public class AppointmentOutcomeService extends Object
The AppointmentOutcomeService class provides methods for managing appointment outcomes, including creating outcomes, dispensing medicines, and retrieving detailed information.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Natalyn Pong
